SYNOPSIS (OPTIONAL)
===================
   #include <idn.h>
   string idna_to_unicode(stringÂ name)

DESCRIPTION
===========
Convert string <name> from idna representation (8z punycode) to UTF-8.

If an error occurs, an exception is thrown.

The efun is available only if the system supports libidn - in that case
__IDNA__ is defined.

Introduced in LDMud 3.3.713.

   See Also:
      convert_charset(E), idna_to_ascii(E), idna_stringprep(E)
